{"type":"message","id":"56536eb3","parentId":"51281047","timestamp":"2026-04-07T03:22:15.992Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_52c78800-0903-4adf-9ded-fb6ebe32f1c0","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/mnt/c/Users/Tiny4Lurv/OneDrive/Apps/Dawn-Restore/GIT_REPO.md","content":"# Git Repository — Dawn Workspace\n\n## Remote\n```\norigin  https://github.com/tiny4lurv/dawn-workspace.git (fetch)\norigin  https://github.com/tiny4lurv/dawn-workspace.git (push)\n```\n\n## Last Commit (Apr 6, 2026)\n```\ncd95c74 Apr 6 memory: Post 1 live, NavaSM rewrite, FB insights, emoji reading, I vs we rule\n```\n\n## Branch\n```\nmain\n```\n\n## To Clone a Fresh Machine\n```bash\ngit clone https://github.com/tiny4lurv/dawn-workspace.git ~/.openclaw/workspace\n```\n\n## Post-Clone Setup\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace\ngit remote -v  # confirm origin\n```\n"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":20125,"output":248,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20373,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775532135990}}
