sted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"3EB05F570E915C407DF155\",\n  \"s\n  System: [2026-04-07 05:30:58 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 408)\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly\n  System: [2026-04-07 07:24:27 GMT+2] Sprint check-in:\nSystem: 1. Check if TrnsBank.md has messages — if yes, wait for Tiny to lock bank before analysin\n  System: [2026-04-07 07:24:42 GMT+2] Morning routine:\nSystem: 1. Read memory/2026-MM-DD.md for today's context\nSystem: 2. Check memory/morning_routine_\n\n=== 7cdffa-4fce-40df-b111-0e1fd501f6b (1 user msgs) ===\n  [cron:4ee0c18c-e191-402f-83c6-a551ed2850b2 Dream Mode — Nightly Reflection] ## Task: Dream Mode — Nightly Reflection\\n\\nYou are running an isolated re","cwd":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775573272479}}
