er by 250 basis points year over year and a decrease of 50 basis points sequentially.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"581680056812b09f\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"February 20, 2025\",\n      \"siteName\": \"last10k.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"61c382b6eb46c1cc\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nUNITED STATES SECURITIES AND EXCHANGE COMMISSION Washington, D.C. 20549\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"61c382b6eb46c1cc\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://ir.amnhealthcare.com/static-files/7153b383-e160-4c8f-9ea3-bcbd4fd69739\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d5d755141dd092be\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAdditionally, individual states often have regulations governing healthcare staffing agencies and technology · platforms, requiring registration and various types of certifications and reporting. Compliance with these laws, rules and regulations has not had, and is not · expected to have, a material effect on our capital expenditures, results of operations, or competitive position. ... We maintain a corporate website at www.amnhealthcare.com.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d5d755141dd092be\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"February 20, 2025\",\n      \"siteName\": \"ir.amnhealthcare.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"AMN Healthcare 10-K SEC filing 2024 revenue margins staffing","provider":"brave","count":5,"tookMs":4552,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"brave","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"99ebc3e5043977ba\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAMN Healthcare Announces Fourth Quarter and Full Year 2024 Results | AMN Healthcare Services Inc.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"99ebc3e5043977ba\">>>","url":"https://ir.amnhealthcare.com/news-releases/news-release-details/amn-healthcare-announces-fourth-quarter-and-full-year-2024","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UN