e margins overnight.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8305b2a0842070e4\">>>","published":"August 6, 2025","siteName":"www.stocktitan.net"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f8f2cda634c4d03a\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAmn Healthcare Services Inc (AMN) 10K Annual Reports & 10Q SEC Filings\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f8f2cda634c4d03a\">>>","url":"https://last10k.com/sec-filings/amn","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"581680056812b09f\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAdjusted EBITDA was $75 million, reflecting a year-over-year decrease of 28%. Adjusted EBITDA margin was <strong>10.2%</strong>, lower by 250 basis points year over year and a decrease of 50 basis points sequentially.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"581680056812b09f\">>>","published":"February 20, 2025","siteName":"last10k.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"61c382b6eb46c1cc\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nUNITED STATES SECURITIES AND EXCHANGE COMMISSION Washington, D.C. 20549\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"61c382b6eb46c1cc\">>>","url":"https://ir.amnhealthcare.com/static-files/7153b383-e160-4c8f-9ea3-bcbd4fd69739","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"d5d755141dd092be\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAdditionally, individual states often have regulations governing healthcare staffing agencies and technology · platforms, requiring registration and various types of certifications and reporting. Compliance with these laws, rules and regulations has not had, and is not · expected to have, a material effect on our capital expenditures, results of operations, or competitive position. ... We maintain a corporate website at www.amnhealthcare.com.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"d5d755141dd092be\">>>","published":"February 20, 2025","siteName":"ir.amnhealthcare.com"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775582948717}}
