ightforward: what is your P&L telling you about whether you are the customer, or the inventory?\n\n---\n\n*Review:* Holds. The spread mechanic, the \"green arrow\" image, the P&L confession from UHS CFO — all the right data in the right order. The CTA lands clean.\n\nWant me to post it, or do you want to revise anything before it goes out?"}],"timestamp":1775584712856}}
