 and stops the cycle. The model was never built for you.\n\n---\n\nThat version has no \"we built NurseSphere,\" Reclaimix gets named with its actual function, and the closer lands without a corporate tagline. Ready to post?"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":71005,"output":486,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71491,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775585103150}}
