ured forensic analysis with public filings, earnings transcripts, and government records citations\n- **Document structured as Tier 1-4 analysis**: Agency economics → Hospital burden → LTC fragility → Government/VA exposure\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Continue reading full ODT text to assess depth and breadth of all four tiers\n2. Evaluate whether each tier could be a standalone blog post\n3. Identify specific statistics and data points that could anchor compelling narratives\n4. Cross-reference with existing Visa Pathway Comparison drafts for potential content synergy\n\n## Critical Context\n- **Primary research file**: `/mnt/c/Users/Tiny4Lurv/Downloads/Healthcare Staffing Value Extraction Analysis.odt` (3,132,521 bytes, downloaded 2026-04-07 19:44)\n- **Key data found so far**:\n  - Market: $39B-$47.3B US healthcare staffing\n  - Top 5 agencies control ~40% of market\n  - Aya Healthcare acquired Cross Country for $615M (Dec 2024), giving Aya ~25% of travel nursing, ~20% of allied staffing\n  - AMN CEO Cary Grace: $62M \"labor disruption revenue\" in Feb 2025 (beat guidance by $22M)\n  - Hospital systems (HCA, Tenet, UHS) tied to agency spend reduction for margin improvement\n  - Tenet Healthcare: contract labor dropped from ~3.5% of SWB (2023) to ~2.1% (2024)\n- **Existing related files**: Healthcare Visa Pathways_ EB-3 vs. TN.pdf, Visa Pathway Comparison v5.md, Travel Nurse Program Research Findings.odt\n- **HTML research files**: Gemini.html (3,047 lines), NewGemini.html (6,072 lines) - contain drafts and AI conversation artifacts\n\n## Recent turns preserved verbatim\n- User: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-04-07 19:28 GMT+2] Give me a deep research prompt (use your skill), to find more information about AMN and other organisations out there that we can mine for actual information.\n- Assistant: [non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (read): ---\nname: deep-research-prompt\ndescription: Generate expert-level deep research prompts for Gemini that produce high-quality Statements of Trade (SoTs). Use when given a topic/theme and asked to create a research prompt that (1) identifies credible sources, (2) surfaces facts over opinions, (3) remains neutral without leaking assumptions, (4) casts a broad net for related useful information, and (5) maintains editorial authority. Triggered by phrases like \"create a research prompt\", \"build a SoT prompt\", \"deep research prompt\", \"write a prompt for Gemini deep research\", \"research this topic fo...\n- Assistant: Doing preliminary research first, then I'll write the prompt.\n[non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (web_search): {\n  \"query\": \"AMN Healthcare 10-K SEC filing 2024 revenue margins staffing\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 4552,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"brave\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"99ebc3e5043977ba\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAMN Healthcare Announces Fourth Quarter and Full Year 2024 Results | AMN Healthcare Services Inc.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"99ebc3e5043977ba\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://ir.amnhealthcare.com/news-releases/new...\n- Assistant: [non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (web_search): {\n  \"query\": \"healthcare staffing agencies publicly traded companies 2024 annual reports revenue profit margins\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 7679,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"brave\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c849d167ade8fadc\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\